                  <div class="thrv_wrapper thrv_text_element" style="" data-css="tve-u-1778cc5643a">
                    <h2 class="" style="text-align: center;">About Bitcoin-Trading</h2>
                    <p>Bitcoin-Trading.io is a portal about cryptocurrencies, Bitcoin, Ethereum and altcoins. We also follow the events in the ICO world. We publish the hottest news, analysts' forecasts, as well as detailed reviews of trading platforms from professional brokers.<br>
                    Our authors are both private crypto brokers and professional licensed brokers who trade on the Nasdaq and NYSE.<br>
                    <br>
                    Keep in mind that trading cryptocurrencies and CFDs are complex instruments. You must understand how tools work and accept the risks they carry.&nbsp; Bitcoin-Trading.io content is not an investment advice.</p>
